    "This involves using renewable energy sources, improving energy efficiency, and implementing carbon offset strategies [76].Research in Green AI focuses on developing environmentally sustainable artificial intelligence technologies [88].",
    "Researchers aim to optimize algorithms, hardware, and data center operations to reduce energy consumption and minimize the carbon footprint of AI systems [91,92].",
    "Techniques such as energy-efficient model training, resourceaware algorithms, and eco-friendly hardware designs are explored [38].",
    "The goal is to create AI solutions that deliver high performance and align with ecological considerations.",
    "This research field contributes to mitigating AI's environmental impact, promoting energy efficiency, and fostering a more sustainable future for artificial intelligence applications."
  ]
}